  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t上传入口：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYmIwMmY3NGJlZjljOTIzY2VkZmNkLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bb02f74bef9c923cedfcd.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bb02f74bef9c923cedfcd.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bb02f74bef9c923cedfcd.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYjdkODgwMDBkNGU5M2UxN2U5ZjY4LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b7d88000d4e93e17e9f68.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b7d88000d4e93e17e9f68.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b7d88000d4e93e17e9f68.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n上传步骤：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMGE2YWJiNGY0NWM0MzM0MTMwYjIzLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0a6abb4f45c4334130b23.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0a6abb4f45c4334130b23.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0a6abb4f45c4334130b23.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n1. 将视频上传至pomf2.lain.la或catbox.moe，点击“Select or drop files”选择文件，上传成功后复制视频链接。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n2. 将视频链接粘贴至下方：<br/>\n<br/>\r\n3. 点击插入按钮，文本框会多出一行代码，请勿修改此行代码。可以通过此方法插入多个视频。<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<b>与推特视频提取器（如<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ2V0bXl0d2VldC5jb20vemgv\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.getmytweet.com/zh/\">getmytweet</a>，<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2F2ZXR3ZWV0dmlkLmNvbS96aA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.savetweetvid.com/zh\">savetweetvid</a>，）配套使用即可将推特视频直接上传至品葱。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n使用例：<br/>\n<br/>\r\n推文链接：https://twitter.com/TruthMedia123/status/1524698398011527168<br/>\r\n提取器：getmytweet<br/>\r\n图床：pomf2.lain.la<br/>\r\n复制推文链接，将推文链接粘贴到提取站的URL文本框中，获得不同格式的下载链接，点击下载链接以mp4格式下载视频。<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYjE4YzM3Yjk1MGFlM2VhNGIyYTJlLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b18c37b950ae3ea4b2a2e.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b18c37b950ae3ea4b2a2e.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b18c37b950ae3ea4b2a2e.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<b>如果单击下载链接时没有发生下载，请右键单击下载链接并选择另存为。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n下载后进行上传。<br/>\r\n上传完成后如图：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMmZkYjc2YzE1NzI3ODJlOGM5MGYxLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2fdb76c1572782e8c90f1.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2fdb76c1572782e8c90f1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2fdb76c1572782e8c90f1.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n右键点击：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvODJjMjI5MzhmMzAxOWJhN2MxY2VjLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/82c22938f3019ba7c1cec.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/82c22938f3019ba7c1cec.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/82c22938f3019ba7c1cec.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n复制视频地址。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n粘贴、插入：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMDc2NTFiMjBhMWRlYjkzNzUxZWRjLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/07651b20a1deb93751edc.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/07651b20a1deb93751edc.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/07651b20a1deb93751edc.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<div class=\"ab-player\"><div class=\"ab-video\"><video controls=\"\" preload=\"metadata\" src=\"https://pomf2.lain.la/f/oowip6qe.mp4\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></video> </div></div> </div>",
